# Force pi0 to always undergo the Dalitz decay pi0 -> e+ e- gamma,
# using EvtGen's PI0_DALITZ model (Kroll-Wada QED matrix element).
# This overrides the default DECAY.DEC branching fractions (which are
# ~98.8% gamma gamma, ~1.2% e+ e- gamma) so that every generated pi0
# is a Dalitz decay, for high-statistics comparison against Geant4.

Decay pi0
1.0  e+ e- gamma  PI0_DALITZ;
Enddecay

End
